28:54.968 --> 28:55.904
Just think.

28:55.937 --> 28:58.074
Remember.

28:58.108 --> 29:00.947
Remember when we made hash in
Mr. Thanski's chemistry class

29:00.980 --> 29:03.318
and the school
almost called the DEA on us?

29:03.351 --> 29:05.489
‐Chad.
‐Hold on.

29:05.523 --> 29:06.825
Quinn.

29:06.859 --> 29:08.829
Okay? Think.

29:08.863 --> 29:12.036
Or when, uh,
when Milo was watching porn

29:12.069 --> 29:13.338
and he
accidentally Bluetoothed it

29:13.371 --> 29:14.875
to the school intercom.
Do you remember that?

29:15.877 --> 29:16.946
Quinn.

29:16.979 --> 29:18.248
Look at me, man.

29:19.518 --> 29:21.454
