29:49.276 --> 29:51.982
Let's find a car,

29:52.016 --> 29:53.819
and let's hunt
this fucking director down.

30:05.275 --> 30:07.947
Yeah, that's the van.

30:07.981 --> 30:12.289
Who lives in a trailer
and drives a Rolls‐Royce?

30:12.323 --> 30:15.228
‐
‐Let's find out.

30:29.190 --> 30:30.993
One officer was quoted as saying

30:31.027 --> 30:33.933
the carnage is unlike anything
he's ever seen.

30:33.966 --> 30:35.870
Now, there are
unconfirmed reports

30:35.903 --> 30:38.876
of attacks spreading into
the surrounding neighborhoods,

30:38.909 --> 30:41.414
but so far,
no one will go on record

30:41.447 --> 30:43.919
as to exactly what
has happened here.

30:43.953 --> 30:46.024
I kicked ass is what happened.

30:46.057 --> 30:48.929
Cinema fucking history
is what happened!

30:48.963 --> 30:50.900
...at least 100 people...

30:50.933 --> 30:52.403
The chickens didn't
just come home to roost...

30:55.977 --> 30:57.146
Who the hell are you?

30:57.179 --> 30:59.150
The chickens, I guess.

30:59.183 --> 31:01.054
You must be Larry Bitterman.

31:01.087 --> 31:04.060
‐What is this?
‐We were there last night.

31:04.093 --> 31:06.230
At the Starlite Drive‐In.

31:06.264 --> 31:08.368
To see your movie.

31:08.401 --> 31:11.040
I don't... I don't know
what you're talking about.

31:11.074 --> 31:14.080
Trust us, that is not the road
that you want to take.

31:14.113 --> 31:15.917
‐We've had a long night.
‐

31:15.950 --> 31:18.054
Okay, take it easy.

31:18.088 --> 31:20.292
What is it?
Just tell me what you want.

31:20.325 --> 31:21.929
We want the other print.

31:21.962 --> 31:23.298
The other print?

31:23.331 --> 31:25.035
For the screening tonight.

31:25.068 --> 31:26.939
Oh, I'm sorry to say
you've been misinformed.

31:26.972 --> 31:28.108
That...

31:28.141 --> 31:30.947
That was a one‐time‐only event.

31:30.980 --> 31:32.449
That was
the last and final print.

31:32.483 --> 31:33.986
I promise.

31:34.019 --> 31:35.623
‐It was on 4chan.
‐

31:35.656 --> 31:38.629
Which means that you're
the last people on earth

31:38.662 --> 31:39.965
who believe
what's on the Internet.

31:39.998 --> 31:41.367
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

31:41.400 --> 31:43.071
If you were at the drive‐in
watching the movie,

31:43.104 --> 31:45.142
why weren't...
I mean, why aren't you...?

31:47.146 --> 31:49.116
You weren't even

31:49.150 --> 31:51.087
paying attention, were you?
You were too busy

31:51.120 --> 31:52.590
laying pipe.

31:52.624 --> 31:54.126
See, this is why
I hated the idea

31:54.160 --> 31:56.097
of premiering at a drive‐in.

31:56.130 --> 31:58.368
